@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<pre>
    🔒 Privacy Policy
    Effective Date: [Insert Date]

    Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services. Please read this policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms, please do not use our services.

    📘 Information We Collect
    We may collect the following types of information:

    Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, and other identifiers.

    Usage Data: Pages visited, time spent, clicks, and other analytics.

    Device Information: IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.

    Cookies and Tracking Technologies: To enhance user experience and analyze usage.

    🛠 How We Use Your Information
    We use the information we collect to:

    Provide and maintain our services

    Improve user experience and functionality

    Communicate with you, including sending updates and promotional content

    Ensure security and prevent fraud

    Comply with legal obligations

    🔄 Sharing Your Information
    We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with:

    Service Providers who help us operate our business

    Legal Authorities when required by law

    Business Transfers in case of a merger or acquisition

    ⚙️ Your Choices
    You can:

    Opt out of marketing communications

    Disable cookies through your browser settings

    Request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data

    🛡 Data Security
    We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

    🌍 International Data Transfers
    If you are located outside of [Your Country], your information may be transferred to and processed in countries with different data protection laws.

    👶 Children's Privacy
    Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

    📞 Contact Us
    If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: Email: [Insert Contact Email] Address: [Insert Company Address]
</pre>
